      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Mehta, Murat, and Allison write [CITATION_1] , \"Many papers aimed at the high-dimensional biology community describe the development or application of statistical techniques. The validity of many of these is questionable, and a shared understanding about the epistemological foundations of the statistical methods themselves seems to be lacking.\""
    }
